But they are not even aware. They don't know.

400
00:28:08,615 --> 00:28:20,479
So, these fabrications, Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta'ala wills that they exist in the world, in order to tell us whether I am a real believer or a false believer.

401
00:28:21,942 --> 00:28:27,340
وَلِتَصْغَىٰٓ إِلَيْهِ أَفْـِٔدَةُ ٱلَّذِينَ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ بِٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ وَلِيَرْضَوْهُ
(6:113) وَلِيَقْتَرِفُوا۟ مَا هُم مُّقْتَرِفُونَ

402
