484
00:33:28,742 --> 00:33:30,223
[69:39]  And what you do not see.

485
00:33:30,223 --> 00:33:32,223
Now, there's nothing stronger than that.

486
00:33:32,998 --> 00:33:40,190
God, Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta'ala is swearing
by what you see, everything you see, and everything you do not see.

487
00:33:40,190 --> 00:33:42,190
