00:50:24,522 --> 00:50:29,392
Even though Allah Subhanahu
Wa Ta'ala gives them 4 steps, they have 9 steps.

660
00:50:29,392 --> 00:50:35,961
So, they better be prepared on the Day of Judgment to answer that question from Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta'ala when He tells them

661
00:50:35,961 --> 00:50:39,510
"I have given you 4 steps of Wudu, why did you do 9?"

662
00:50:40,322 --> 00:50:47,694
You better be ready to answer that. Who is
the other god that told them to do 9 steps in Wudu instead of 4?

663
00:50:48,449 --> 00:50:55,405
Because Allah Subhanahu Wa Ta'ala told them 4 steps. There is some other god, whoever it is, who told them to do 9 steps.

664
00:50:56,679 --> 00:51:01,322
Dr. Khalifa: So, washing the feet is clearly stated in the
Wudu, Sura number 5, verse 6.

665
00:51:03,776 --> 00:51:08,277
Ray Caton: Can Muslims give their organs or blood as
donations?

666
00:51:08,891 --> 00:51:13,864
Dr. Khalifa: Yes, definitely, because the body is not important
at all. Once we leave the body,

667
00:51:13,864 --> 00:51:21,764
the body is like a garment that we are wearing, and if it is going to help another human being, by all means go ahead and do it.

668
00:51:22,898 --> 00:51:27,721
Just like if you take off your shirt, an old
shirt, and you're gonna throw it away,

669
00:51:27,721 --> 00:51:31,609
then you worry about if somebody is gonna take the sleeve or the collar or what.

670
00:51:34,205 --> 00:51:35,119
Dr. Khalifa: That's it.

671
00:51:35,566 --> 00:51:38,879
Ray Caton: And last question is freedom of choice.

672
00:51:39,304 --> 00:51:40,445
Thank you.

673
00:51:40,728 --> 00:51:45,173
God tells us that He can guide whom He wants
and mislead whom He wants.

674
00:51:47,100 --> 00:51:54,689
Ray Caton: Why are we created if we don't have, if God
already knows what our destiny is?

675
00:51:54,689 --> 00:52:03,732
Dr. Khalifa: This is a good question. This indicates that God did not create us to see who's gonna believe and who's not, who will not believe.

676
00:52:05,101 --> 00:52:11,396
Because God knows, God happens to know exactly
what every human being is going to do, believe or disbelieve.

677
00:52:12,576 --> 00:52:20,806
The purpose of our creation here is to, goes back
to the time when Satan wanted to be a god besides God.

678
00:52:22,128 --> 00:52:33,284
And God decided to give Satan a dominion and constituents to prove Satan's incompetence as a god.

679
00:52:33,945 --> 00:52:42,505
So, the human beings who set up a god besides
God, they automatically become members of Satan's kingdom,

680
00:52:42,505 --> 00:52:48,564
subject to his incompetence
and subject to the disasters and problems that go along with that.

681
00:52:49,366 --> 00:52:56,180
So, we have the absolute freedom of choice.
This is one of the conditions

682
00:52:56,180 --> 00:53:04,448
for providing Satan with constituents, that we are absolutely
free to choose God as our god or Satan as our god.

683
00:53:04,448 --> 00:53:12,321
People who set up other gods besides God are
choosing, automatically choosing Satan as their god.

684
00:53:12,530 --> 00:53:15,112
And we see, we see this in Sura number 36,

685
00:53:15,112 --> 00:53:18,510
(36:60) أَلَمْ أَعْهَدْ إِلَيْكُمْ يَـٰبَنِىٓ ءَادَمَ أَن لَّا تَعْبُدُوا۟ ٱلشَّيْطَـٰنَ

686
00:53:18,510 --> 00:53:23,869
[36:60]  Did I not covenant with you, O Children of Adam, that you shall not worship the Satan? ...

687
00:53:24,530 --> 00:53:28,665
So, we are either worshipping God or worshipping
Satan.

688
00:53:28,665 --> 00:53:39,187
And we worship Satan when we support his point of view of having a god besides God, any other idol besides God, proves Satan's point of view.

689
00:53:39,187 --> 00:53:45,671
Now, once we make our free choice decision
to believe or disbelieve,

690
00:53:45,671 --> 00:53:52,097
only God knows what our hearts have decided, what our innermost
convictions are.

691
00:53:52,097 --> 00:53:57,387
And based on our decision, God will either
create circumstances to guide us,

692
00:53:57,387 --> 00:54:05,237
if we decide to choose him as our god, or will create circumstances
to augment our disbelief and our idolworship,

693
00:54:05,237 --> 00:54:10,487
if we decide to idolize someone else besides
God.

694
00:54:12,658 --> 00:54:14,655
Dr. Khalifa: So, this should answer all the questions, I
guess.

695
00:54:15,080 --> 00:54:16,331
Ray Caton: Yes, thank you very much.

696
00:54:16,331 --> 00:54:17,887
Dr. Khalifa: You're welcome. Alhamdu Lillah.